originalText.text: Ruslan was our tour guide in NYC. He was very friendly,helpful and knowledgeable for two days touring New York. Thank you. Highly recommended

originalText.text:
Highly recommended! We took two walking tours with my 72 year old mom. It was very interesting, personal and not exhausting. All the friends were amazed by how many places we were able to see in a short time!

originalText.text: I took my staff to a guided tour with this tour agency in NYC and it was amazing! Not only did the guide canceled his plans for the evening to take us on a tour at the very last minute, but it ended up being one of the best guided trips that we have ever done. The guide  is a friendly and funny person, filled with interesting information and you can tell that he really loves what she does. I have a dental office in Ohio and I do take my staff for travel every now and then and this last trip in NYC was very enjoyable and pleasant. Thanks

originalText.text: The experience we had was beyond perfect. Rus is filled with interesting information and you can tell that he really loves what he does. As I'm a photographer Rus was very happy to morph the tour into exactly what I wanted, happily timing our trip perfectly so I could photograph the sunset from a perfect vantage point. I would recommend him and his guided tours to everyone. Just amazing!!!!!:)
